title: The Drinker Fixes... The Multiverse Of Madness
description:
Doctor Strange In The Multiverse Of Madness was an absolute mess of a story that ruined not one but two great characters in the MCU. But could it have been better? Was there a way to salvage it? Join me as I do my best to work the Drinker magic on it.
